                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.00/844.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Consul at Santiago</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase. ]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santiago, Cuba</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-06-28T06:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 28, 1912—6 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The rebel leader Estenoz was killed yesterday in a battle at Micara. His body was
                    brought here and positively identified.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Holaday</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
